data.description: This well-kept, low maintenance full brick home located on a cul-de-sac, features a metal roof, energy efficient windows throughout, with open living and dining rooms as well as a main level den with custom built in cabinetry. It has a huge covered and screened deck with storage space underneath. It has a large, fenced back yard with an enormous garage which consists of tall double doors. Located behind the garage is a covered carport. Come see it today.
